Show HN: France/Belgium interactive trip using Mapbox GL JS
text:
Hey HN!

I'm a college student studying Computer/Data Science and I love creating interactive stories about my experiences! I've been interested in web development for years now and I recently created this project as a gift to commemorate my recent trip to France/Belgium with my girlfriend.

I was also able to identify and propose some solutions for a Mapbox GL JS bug while working on this project! It doesn't currently work on mobile devices, but I hope you find it as satisfying as I do on your computer.

Thanks! - Matthew
